snippet.title: The Day We Fought Space - Date Announce!
snippet.description:
The Day We Fought Space, a wreck-em-up with spiraling chain reactions and over-the-top physics-fueled weapons, coming to the App Store May 26th!

Pre-order now at https://apps.apple.com/us/app/the-day-we-fought-space/id1015736502

Follow us on Twitter for screenshots and dev updates: https://twitter.com/TursiopsStudios
Join our Discord community for beta access: Discord: https://discord.gg/KDGvtwR
Sign up for our newsletter at http://www.thedaywefoughtspace.com/
Follow us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TursiopsTruncatusStudios
See more from Tursiops Truncatus Studios at http://tursiopsstudios.com/
